name: Black & White Ball AI Tile 1
description: This an AI-generated color version of my black and white digital work, "Black AND White Ball." I do love surreal environments, because that is how I see the world! Conventional paintings always puzzle me. Is that all the artist sees when looking at a scene, a subject? No thoughts, no associations, no metaphors, no ideas? Everything I see is dense with meaning, a network of many nodes. I try to convey that feeling in my work.
